cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the zero correlation zone config to 100 exceeds the valid range (0-15), leading to improper PRACH configuration and RACH failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將零相關區配置設定為 100 超過有效範圍 (0-15)，導致 PRACH 配置不當，並造成 RACH 失敗。
